OL,7, Taliban toppled in 2001 and his country
OL,8, transformed. But in his view, as he
OL,9, explains here, the US missed an
OL,10, opportunity to try to bring lasting
OL,11, peace. And in the last two weeks the
OL,12, path of his homeland took a terrifying
OL,13, twist, one that put his own life in
OL,14, danger.
